{
  "stem": "17426.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 38.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then I tried with all my power to get closer, that I can intercept it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I almost did, except I was still away about 100 feet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I begged them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I said, please take me on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Oh, we have no more room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We can't take anybody on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There were 10 or 12 naked inmates already in the boat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I was naked too, because I left all my things go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And suddenly, somebody yelled out, this is our dentist.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Let's take him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How many miracles did one need to survive?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sometime, miracles-- sometime you need it more even than miracles.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was more than a miracle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so they pulled me in, and I lay there in pain because my last relative-- my brother, to whom I was very close, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and who was very close to me-- I thought I'll never see again.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The fishermen brought us to the shore, and we stepped out on the sand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we looked around and assessed our chances.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're going to be caught and brought to another concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Worse even, brought on another ship or even shot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] We asked the fishermen where we should go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oh, he says.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Go down a little bit up the hill.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You'll see a house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There's a bakery.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You might find some bread there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I think, he says, the owner of the bakery probably left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But you may find at least something to house you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were naked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was 5 o'clock in the afternoon by the time I was in shore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We walked, and we saw inmates on the shore, washed ashore dead.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
